## P1: Secret Management

### Problem
Secrets are still scattered. Production needs unified management.

### Work Required

| Task | Status | Owner |
|------|--------|-------|
| Document secret rotation policy | ✅ Complete (in SECRETS.md) | Agent B |
| Audit all env vars for secret leakage | ✅ Complete | Agent B |
| Add secret masking to all loggers | � Partial (identified issues) | Agent B |
| Create `docs/operations/SECRETS.md` runbook | ✅ Complete | Agent B |
| Fix plaintext passwords in service files | 🔴 Not started | Agent B |
| Remove hardcoded default passwords from Python | 🔴 Not started | Agent B |
| Remove default passwords from database URLs | 🔴 Not started | Agent B |
| Standardize on `/etc/aitbc/%N.env` pattern | 🔴 Not started | DevOps |

### Audit Findings

**CRITICAL (Fix immediately):**
- `apps/blockchain-node/aitbc-blockchain-p2p.service:14` — `MEMPOOL_DB_URL=...aitbc_mempool_password...`
- `apps/governance/aitbc-governance.service:17` — `Environment="DB_PASS=aitbc_governance_pass"`

**HIGH (Fix before production):**
- `aitbc/training_setup/cli.py:124` — `default="training123"`
- `aitbc/training_setup/blockchain.py:111` — `password: str = "training123"`
- `aitbc/training_setup/environment.py:150` — `password: str = "training123"`
- `apps/agent-coordinator/src/app/routers/auth.py:36-38` — fallback defaults `admin123`, `operator123`, `user123`

**MEDIUM:**
- `apps/ai-engine/examples/src/aitbc_ai/storage.py:11` — default password in connection string
- `apps/coordinator-api/migrations/003_data_migration.py:197` — default password in migration script

**LOW:**
- `apps/blockchain-node/scripts/create_genesis_wallet.py:91-92` — prints private key and password to stdout
- `apps/blockchain-node/scripts/keystore.py:105-134` — prints keystore info to stdout

**GOOD PRACTICES (maintain):**
- `EnvironmentFile=/run/aitbc/secrets/.env` used by blockchain-node and coordinator-api
- Only `.env.example` files committed (no real `.env` files in Git)
- `dev/validator_keys.json` replaced with template + generation script

### Files
- `docs/operations/SECRETS.md` — Complete runbook with findings, migration plan, rotation policy, and verification script

### Acceptance Criteria
- [x] Secret audit completed and documented
- [x] Secret rotation policy documented
- [x] Migration plan created with phased approach
- [ ] No plaintext secrets in service files
- [ ] No hardcoded default passwords in code
- [ ] No default passwords in database URLs
- [ ] All secrets in `/etc/aitbc/` or `/run/aitbc/secrets/`

